<div class="about-wrap">
  <div class="container pt20 pb20">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
        <div class="about-content">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <p>由SparkleBritain Ltd.出品的<span class="site-name">英国老帽儿</span>是一个集结了英国生活方式、人物、景点、物产和设计创意等方方面面精华的平台，其总部设在英国伦敦，中国办公室设在北京。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                  <%= image_tag 'frontend/logo/sparkle.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
