          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
        <div class="about-content">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <p>在此献上<%= link_to raw('<span class="site-name">《英国老帽儿》</span>团队'), experts_path %>的美好祝福！</p>
